channel.title: ASF Jira

item.title: [HIVE-7229] String is compared using equal in HiveMetaStore#HMSHandler#init()
item.description:
Around line 423:

      if (partitionValidationRegex != null && partitionValidationRegex != "") {
        partitionValidationPattern = Pattern.compile(partitionValidationRegex);

partitionValidationRegex.isEmpty() can be used instead.
item.summary: String is compared using equal in HiveMetaStore#HMSHandler#init()

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
